        <ul class="mt-10 space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-700">
          <li>✅ Up to 10 customized agents, integrated with each other.</li>
          <li>✅ Custom architecture and development.</li>
          <li>✅ Connection to internal APIs or ERP-type systems.</li>
          <li>✅ Custom analytics dashboards + advanced logs.</li>
          <li>✅ Dedicated technical support.</li>
          <li>
